{"parse":{"title":"free time","pageid":33831,"redirects":[],"wikitext":"==English==\n{{wp|Leisure}}\n\n===Pronunciation===\n* {{audio|en|LL-Q1860 (eng)-Vealhurl-free time.wav|a=Southern England}}\n\n===Noun===\n{{en-noun|-}}\n\n# Time when one is not [[work]]ing.\n#: {{syn|en|spare time|leisure time|leisure|downtime|idle time||alt6=one's own time<!--not idiomatic; do not wikify-->}}\n#: {{ux|en|I love to play football in my '''free time'''.}}\n#: {{ux|en|If you have some '''free time''' tomorrow, let’s go and watch a film.}}\n\n====Translations====\n{{trans-top-see|time when one is not working|time off}}\n* Afrikaans: {{t|af|vrye tyd}}\n* Arabic: {{t|ar|رَاحَة|f}}, {{t|ar|خُلُو مِنَ الْعَمَل}}, {{t|ar|فَرَاغ|m}}, {{t|ar|وَقْت الْفَرَاغ|m}}\n* Bashkir: {{t|ba|буш ваҡыт}}\n* Belarusian: {{t|be|свабо́дны час|m}}\n* Bulgarian: {{t|bg|свобо́дно вре́ме|n}}\n* Catalan: {{t+|ca|oci|m}}, {{t|ca|temps lliure|m}}\n* Chinese:\n*: Mandarin: {{t+|cmn|空閑|tr=kòngxián}}, {{t|cmn|閑空|tr=xiánkòng}}, {{t+|cmn|閑暇|tr=xiánxiá}}, {{t+|cmn|餘暇|tr=yúxiá}}, {{t+|cmn|餘閑|tr=yúxián}}, {{qualifier|informal}} {{t+|cmn|空兒|tr=kòngr}}\n* Czech: {{t|cs|volný čas|m}}\n* Danish: {{t+|da|fritid|c}}\n* Dutch: {{t+|nl|vrije tijd|m}}\n* Finnish: {{t+|fi|vapaa-aika}}\n* French: {{t+|fr|temps libre|m}}, {{t+|fr|loisir|m}}\n* Galician: {{t|gl|lecer|m}}, {{t|gl|ocio|m}}, {{t|gl|tempo libre|m}}, {{t+|gl|vagar|m}}\n* Georgian: {{t|ka|თავისუფალი დრო}}, {{t|ka|მოცალეობის ჟამი}}\n* German: {{t+|de|Freizeit|f}}\n* Greek: {{t+|el|ελεύθερος χρόνος}}\n*: Ancient Greek: {{t|grc|σχολή|f}}\n* Hebrew: {{t+|he|פְּנַאי|m|tr=p'náy}}\n* Hungarian: {{t+|hu|szabadidő}}\n* Ingrian: {{t|izh|joutava aika}}\n* Italian: {{t|it|tempo libero|m}}, {{t|it|tempi morti|m-p}}\n* Japanese: {{t+|ja|余暇|tr=よか, yoka}}, {{t+|ja|閑暇|tr=かんか, kanka}}, {{t+|ja|閑散|tr=かんさん, kansan}}, {{t+|ja|暇|tr=ひま, hima}}\n* Kazakh: {{t|kk|бос уақыт}}\n* Korean: {{t+|ko|여가(餘暇)}}\n* Latin: {{t|la|ōtium|n}}\n* Macedonian: {{t|mk|сло́бодно вре́ме|n}}\n* Malay: {{t|ms|masa lapang}}, {{t|ms|masa lega}}\n* Manchu: {{t|mnc|ᡧᠣᠯᠣ}}, {{t|mnc|ᠵᠠᠪᡩᡠᡤᠠᠨ}}\n* Norwegian:\n*: Bokmål: {{t+|nb|fritid|m|f}}\n*: Nynorsk: {{t|nn|fritid|f}}\n* Old English: {{t|ang|ǣmethwīl|f}}\n* Persian:\n*: Iranian Persian: {{t+|fa-ira|اُوقاتِ فَراغَت}}\n* Polish: {{t+|pl|czas wolny|m}}, {{t+|pl|wolne|n}}, {{t+|pl|laba|f}}\n* Portuguese: {{t+|pt|folga|f}}, {{t|pt|tempo livre|m}}\n* Romanian: {{t|ro|timp liber}}, {{t+|ro|răgaz|n}}\n* Russian: {{t|ru|свобо́дное вре́мя|n}}, {{t+|ru|досу́г|m}}\n* Serbo-Croatian:\n*: Cyrillic: {{t|sh|слободно време|n}}\n*: Latin: {{t|sh|slobodno vreme|n}}\n* Slovak: {{t|sk|voľný čas|m}}\n* Slovene: {{t|sl|prosti čas|m}}\n* Southern Altai: {{t|alt|бош ӧй}}\n* Spanish: {{t|es|tiempo libre|m}}, {{t+|es|ocio|m}}, {{t|es|tiempo ocio|m}}\n* Swedish: {{t+|sv|fritid|c}}\n* Turkish: {{t+|tr|boş zaman}}, {{t+|tr|boş zaman|p|alt=boş zamanlar}}\n* Ukrainian: {{t|uk|ві́льний час|m}}\n{{trans-bottom}}\n\n{{C|en|Time}}"}}